    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_7_2206-2245",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2206-2245",
      "markText": "“来吧，您先喝。我担心，手放进去会搅浑水，而且在女人后面喝不干净。”阿妈说道。",
      "totalCount": 1547,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2206&rangeEnd=2245",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2206&rangeEnd=2245"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_6_4470-4543",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4470-4543",
      "markText": "我对他们既没有好奇，也不蔑视，完全忘记他们是巡回艺人这种下等职业了。我这种超乎寻常的善意似乎深深地沁入了他们的内心，希望我有空去大岛他们的家里去。",
      "totalCount": 1404,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4470&rangeEnd=4543",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4470&rangeEnd=4543"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_8_1978-2038",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1978-2038",
      "markText": "我胳膊肘撑在窗台上，久久凝望着夜晚的街景。这是一条黑暗的街道。我感觉远处不断传来微弱的鼓声，不由得泪水扑簌簌地滑落下来。",
      "totalCount": 1328,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1978&rangeEnd=2038",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1978&rangeEnd=2038"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_4_3984-4006",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3984-4006",
      "markText": "我心中烦恼异常，心想那舞女今晚不会被糟蹋吧？",
      "totalCount": 1275,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3984&rangeEnd=4006",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3984&rangeEnd=4006"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_3_1987-2037",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1987-2037",
      "markText": "那些书信和药袋他也不舍得扔掉，全堆在身边，成天望着它们过日子。年复一年，那些破旧的废纸就堆积成山了。",
      "totalCount": 1066,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1987&rangeEnd=2037",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1987&rangeEnd=2037"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_3_386-441",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "386-441",
      "markText": "山路变得曲曲折折，眼看就要到天城山的山顶了。这时，大雨把茂密的杉树林笼罩成白花花的一片，从山脚快速地向我逼近。",
      "totalCount": 960,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=441",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=441"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_3_3288-3334",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3288-3334",
      "markText": "走进黑黢黢的隧道，冰冷的水珠滴滴答答地落下来。前方渐渐露出了些许亮光，那是通往南伊豆的出口。",
      "totalCount": 944,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3288&rangeEnd=3334",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3288&rangeEnd=3334"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_7_3634-3695",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3634-3695",
      "markText": "途中，各个村的入口处都立着一块牌子。 ——乞丐、巡回艺人禁止进村。",
      "totalCount": 803,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3634&rangeEnd=3695",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3634&rangeEnd=3695"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_3_2646-2665",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2646-2665",
      "markText": "既然如此，那就让舞女今晚住我房间里吧。",
      "totalCount": 740,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2646&rangeEnd=2665",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2646&rangeEnd=2665"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_7_2526-2568",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2526-2568",
      "markText": "在汤野的时候，我曾打算把舞女插在前额的梳子要来，所以看她用来梳狗毛，我觉得很不舒服。",
      "totalCount": 737,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2526&rangeEnd=2568",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2526&rangeEnd=2568"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_4_2077-2114",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2077-2114",
      "markText": "这番出乎意外的话，使我幡然醒悟。山顶上被老婆婆煽动起来的幻想顿时烟消云散。",
      "totalCount": 704,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2077&rangeEnd=2114",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2077&rangeEnd=2114"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_3_1287-1381",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1287-1381",
      "markText": "——那天在修善寺，今晚来汤岛，明天大概要越过天城山往南前往汤野温泉吧。在天城山二十多公里的山路上一定能追上她们。我抱着这样的幻想，急匆匆赶路而来，没想到在避雨的茶馆正好碰上，心里激动不已。",
      "totalCount": 696,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1287&rangeEnd=1381",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1287&rangeEnd=1381"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_9_1128-1183",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1128-1183",
      "markText": "我寻了很多话题与她攀谈，可是舞女只是俯首，一味盯着运河入海处，一言不发。有几次我话还没说完，她就一个劲儿点头。",
      "totalCount": 666,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1128&rangeEnd=1183",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1128&rangeEnd=1183"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_4_444-489",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "444-489",
      "markText": "走了不到七百米，我就追上了他们。但我又不能突然放慢脚步，便佯装冷漠的样子从舞女们身旁走过。",
      "totalCount": 658,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=444&rangeEnd=489",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=444&rangeEnd=489"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_9_845-935",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "845-935",
      "markText": "快接近码头时，舞女蹲在海边的身影撞入了我的心头。直到走到近旁她依然一动不动，默默地耷拉着头。还是昨晚的妆容，这更加牵动了我的心。眼梢的红晕为略带愠色的脸庞增添了一抹稚嫩的凛然之色。",
      "totalCount": 598,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=845&rangeEnd=935",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=845&rangeEnd=935"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_4_2854-2887",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2854-2887",
      "markText": "我想，他大概是出于好奇或者爱上了卖艺的姑娘，才帮忙拿行李跟了来的。",
      "totalCount": 595,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2854&rangeEnd=2887",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2854&rangeEnd=2887"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_6_2819-2847",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2819-2847",
      "markText": "纯朴而亲切的旅馆老板娘告诫我说，请这样的人吃饭，不值得。",
      "totalCount": 572,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2819&rangeEnd=2847",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2819&rangeEnd=2847"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_9_2385-2420",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2385-2420",
      "markText": "无论别人对我多么亲切，我都欣然接受，我内心生出一种美好而又空虚的情绪。",
      "totalCount": 560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300046683&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2385&rangeEnd=2420",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e8732d70813ab78bcg013ecf?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2385&rangeEnd=2420"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300046683_4_4097-4136",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4097-4136",
      "markText": "我心想，即使赤脚冲出浴池赶到那边去，也是无济于事的。那时，已是凌晨两点多钟了。",
